text:
[Verse]
Heart beating fast now
Love running wild
Caught in a whirlpool
Spinning all around

[Verse 2]
Phone lights up bright
Message just from you
Can't help but smile wide
Feeling something true

[Chorus]
Heart over heels
Dancing in the streets
Love what I feel
Everyone can see

[Verse 3]
Sky painted blue
Dreams starting to grow
Hand in my hand
Never letting go

[Verse 4]
Voice whispers close
Serenade of dreams
Lost in the night
Caught up in the scene

[Chorus]
Heart over heels
Dancing in the streets
Love what I feel
Everyone can see
title: Heart Over Heels
